{"tid":1497880,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"Google證實中共企圖操縱「香港示威」輿論,  美國國務院 : 深感憂心","createTime":"2019-08-23T07:18:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-26T14:46:57.000Z","uid":134071,"like":681,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":99,"replies":[{"pid":"db479ff9818d1c360539df6a983a7d7f33b7b285","tid":1497880,"uid":134071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:18:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.inside.com.tw/article/17297-youtube-blocking-chinese-fake-information-channels\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inside.com.tw%2Farticle%2F17297-youtube-blocking-chinese-fake-information-channels&d=d0UHt22HnArKS4Vgrvpv1XHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=df273f0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.inside.com.tw/article/17297-youtube-blocking-chinese-fake-information-channels</a><br />\n<br />\n封鎖 210 頻道！YouTube：中國企圖操縱香港反送中輿論<br />\n2019/08/23  中央社<br />\n<br />\n科技巨擘 Alphabet Inc 的谷歌（Google）今天宣布，旗下影音串流服務平台 YouTube 已關閉 210 個頻道，這些頻道顯然針對香港抗議活動展開「協同影響行動」，企圖操縱輿論。<br />\n<br />\n數天前，推特（Twitter）和臉書（Facebook）才表示已破獲源自中國的類似活動，宣布停權並刪除可疑帳號。<br />\n<br />\n<strong>Google 網路安全主管之一的杭特利（Shane Huntley）在網誌發文指出：「這項發現與臉書和推特宣布近日與中國有關的觀察和行動相符。」</strong><br />\n<br />\n推特和臉書 19 日指出，他們移除的頻道和帳號從事中國在背後支持的動作，透過發文指稱參與示威的民眾是危險且惡劣的極端主義分子，藉此破壞香港抗爭行動。<br />\n<br />\n香港自 6 月爆發「反送中」抗議，至今演變為更大規模的爭取民主活動，這種局勢發展已成為中國領導人習近平 2012 年掌權以來面臨的最大挑戰之一。<br />\n<br />\n美國國務院發言人告訴路透社：「我們對中國透過散布有關香港局勢的虛假訊息以企圖操縱輿論深感憂心。」<br />\n<br />\n推特、臉書和 YouTube 全遭中國政府禁止使用，但在香港可使用。這些網路平台嚴禁欺騙性做法和假帳號。<br />\n<br />\n推薦閱讀：Google 被控與中國政府合作 川普：將會調查<br />\n<br />\n然而，這 3 家公司也因在中國創造所得和提供國營媒體和官員服務，遭到網友批評。<br />\n<br />\n    責任編輯：Mia"},{"pid":"de9078c4d2d1f26aea86b1bafad484d8b1fc67c6","tid":1497880,"uid":134071,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:18:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b977053efe676f2a93afda0193ec01be9b1137b","tid":1497880,"uid":134071,"like":89,"dislike":1,"score":88,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:20:10.000Z","msg":"Twitte, Facebook, Google都忍唔住出聲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e88562e77187494971ae6635360eb717679143c8","tid":1497880,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:20:35.000Z","msg":"pppp"},{"pid":"9d21a8a27e34f2235a8c29e4c01633dc07b500be","tid":1497880,"uid":263161,"like":23,"dislike":3,"score":20,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:21:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f746e297fbd61bf8c5dc05cc6256e746105f58f9","tid":1497880,"uid":263161,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:21:17.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"319c999701dd97ca39eb34167b30c5624d663bef","tid":1497880,"uid":67454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:22:05.000Z","msg":"幾時向中國宣戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"49cbb49a64de065df6362b3eb0fe4387c3f56b47","tid":1497880,"uid":27793,"like":25,"dislike":0,"score":25,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:22:31.000Z","msg":"有無獨立一個舉報option<br />\n方便我地幫youtube手<br />\n<br />\n怡嬸假新聞youtuber<br />\n一係就扭曲事實<br />\n對美國非常不利"},{"pid":"ddf739d13c59f0686c2e5c25fab4065b5d9ea6c2","tid":1497880,"uid":212626,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:23:52.000Z","msg":"強烈不滿和堅決反對Google同美國對中國事務說三道四、顛倒黑白、煽風點火、粗暴干涉、指手劃腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"183f74d389256a0d301976a1a11f083c049643d1","tid":1497880,"uid":134071,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T07:24:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>B612星人 =報導cctvb假新聞, 死不悔改<br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://na.cx/i/essgx2h.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%